Hey, nobody's
even watching us!

142
00:07:58,541 --> 00:08:01,208
Inada! Commentate
on our thumb-war!

143
00:08:01,291 --> 00:08:02,208
[INADA] Why?

144
00:08:02,291 --> 00:08:04,166
