whoever the winner is

174
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:12,250
then I'm totally
king of the hill.

175
00:09:12,333 --> 00:09:13,958
[FUNABORI] I guess
that makes sense,

176
00:09:14,041 --> 00:09:16,166
